
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Welcome to ClusterClear</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f7f7f9;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding:40px 0;background:#f7f7f9;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

  <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;overflow:hidden;max-width:600px;">

    <!-- Header -->
    <tr>
      <td align="center" width="100%" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding:24px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f1f1;background:#ffffff">
        <a href="https://www.clusterclear.app" style="text-decoration:none;">
          <img 
            src="https://i.postimg.cc/J4zBvpSN/newcluster.png"
            alt="ClusterClear"
            width="180"
            style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;margin:auto;background:#ffffff">
        </a>
      </td>
    </tr>

    <!-- Body -->
    <tr>
      <td style="padding:40px 36px;color:#222222;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">

        <p style="margin:0 0 18px 0;">Hi {{name}},</p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 18px 0;">
        Thanks for joining the <strong>ClusterClear</strong> waitlist! 🎉 We're excited to have you in our creator community.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 26px 0;">
        By joining, you’ll be among the first to experience how ClusterClear helps you:
        </p>

        <ul style="margin:0 0 26px 20px;padding:0;color:#222222;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
          <li>Get important fan messages filtered so you only see what matters</li>
          <li>Monetize priority messages from fans and collaborators</li>
          <li>Save time and energy while staying engaged with your top supporters</li>
          <li>Be among the first to access new features and tools for creators</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="margin:0 0 26px 0;">
        We’ll notify you as soon as ClusterClear launches, so you can start earning and connecting smarter, not harder.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 26px 0;">
        Until then, keep an eye on your inbox for updates and tips to make the most out of your upcoming experience.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 26px 0;color:#555555;font-size:14px;">
        Thanks again for joining — your priority access means you’re at the front of the line! 🚀
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0;color:#777777;font-size:14px;">
        — The ClusterClear Team
        </p>

      </td>
    </tr>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:22px;background:#6355FF;color:#ffffff;font-size:12px;">
        © {{year}} ClusterClear. All rights reserved.
      </td>
    </tr>

  </table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

